  "lyrics": "Victim of the streets and a victim of my choices Turn to these drugs, now these drugs turn to poisons Voices hoarse, I can hardly speak And I haven't bathed in about 8 weeks And they don't face me I'm addicted, I'm breathing deep On my knees, I'm neglected Snorting speed on my knees, gotta feel helpless Spying is chameleon without purpose Blitz my epidermis, it's fucking hurt From these many colors that I've been turning And that's hopelessness Soaks in skin, I struggle towards the top like dorsal fins Atrocious sins within the dope I spend Longing for something to leave me extinct Yet I remain such an absence of me Possessed by these deeds and this high that I chase This high that I hate, high I'm so high I just wanna deflate I wanna feel safe, I loathe how this succubus calls me a maid I try to digress, but don't need to break Addict at least as a lead No doubt's my most dominant trait I slowly decay No colors no longer, I only see gray Somebody show me the way Don't save me a place with a brimstone in hell I need help from myself, can you tell? Don't save me a place with a brimstone in hell I need help from myself, can you tell? I can't tell Don't save me a place with a brimstone in hell I need help from myself, can you tell? Victim of the streets and a victim of my choices Turn to these drugs, now these drugs turn to poisons Voices, voice, I can hardly speak And I have been bathed in about a week But it don't phase me, I'm a different breed Indeed, all my needs are neglected Snorts me, all my needs Gotta feel helpless Gotta feel helpless I'm on my knees, I'm so unsteady I'm doing everything you told me not to do I knew you were right, I knew I was wrong But I still said, fuck that, I'm gone So come back to me, Succubus And make me the way you thought I should be I need help with me Come back, Succubus Please come back I need help with me The me inside of me Victim of the streets and a victim of my choices Turn to these drugs, now these drugs turn to poisons Voices, voice, I can hardly speak And I have been bathed in about a week But it don't phase me, I'm a different breed Indeed, all my needs are neglected Snorts me, all my needs Gotta feel helpless Gotta feel helpless Victim of the streets and a victim of my choices Turn to these drugs, now these drugs turn to poison Voices, voice, I can hardly speak And I have been bathed in about a week But it don't phase me, I'm a different breed Indeed, all my needs are neglected Snorts me, all my needs Gotta feel helpless Gotta feel helpless 🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥 🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 19.899999618530273,
      "text": "Victim of the streets and a victim of my choices Turn to these drugs, now these drugs turn to poisons",
      "start": 15.819999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 23.700000762939453,
      "text": "Voices hoarse, I can hardly speak And I haven't bathed in about 8 weeks",
      "start": 20.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 26.219999313354492,
      "text": "And they don't face me I'm addicted, I'm breathing deep",
      "start": 23.700000762939453
    },
    {
      "end": 29.6200008392334,
      "text": "On my knees, I'm neglected Snorting speed on my knees, gotta feel helpless",
      "start": 26.219999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 35.560001373291016,
      "text": "Spying is chameleon without purpose Blitz my epidermis, it's fucking hurt",
      "start": 31.760000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 38.779998779296875,
      "text": "From these many colors that I've been turning And that's hopelessness",
      "start": 35.560001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 41.70000076293945,
      "text": "Soaks in skin, I struggle towards the top like dorsal fins",
      "start": 38.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 46.20000076293945,
      "text": "Atrocious sins within the dope I spend Longing for something to leave me extinct",
      "start": 41.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 50.220001220703125,
      "text": "Yet I remain such an absence of me Possessed by these deeds and this high that I chase",
      "start": 46.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 53.15999984741211,
      "text": "This high that I hate, high I'm so high I just wanna deflate",
      "start": 50.220001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 56.18000030517578,
      "text": "I wanna feel safe, I loathe how this succubus calls me a maid",
      "start": 53.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 59.68000030517578,
      "text": "I try to digress, but don't need to break Addict at least as a lead",
      "start": 56.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 62.2400016784668,
      "text": "No doubt's my most dominant trait I slowly decay",
      "start": 59.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 65.72000122070312,
      "text": "No colors no longer, I only see gray Somebody show me the way",
      "start": 62.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 69.23999786376953,
      "text": "Don't save me a place with a brimstone in hell I need help from myself, can you tell?",
      "start": 65.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 73.26000213623047,
      "text": "Don't save me a place with a brimstone in hell I need help from myself, can you tell?",
      "start": 69.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 74.37999725341797,
      "text": "I can't tell",
      "start": 73.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 79.26000213623047,
      "text": "Don't save me a place with a brimstone in hell I need help from myself, can you tell?",
      "start": 75.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 83.87999725341797,
      "text": "Victim of the streets and a victim of my choices Turn to these drugs, now these drugs turn to poisons",
      "start": 80.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 87.68000030517578,
      "text": "Voices, voice, I can hardly speak And I have been bathed in about a week",
      "start": 83.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 91.33999633789062,
      "text": "But it don't phase me, I'm a different breed Indeed, all my needs are neglected",
      "start": 87.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 93.80000305175781,
      "text": "Snorts me, all my needs Gotta feel helpless",
      "start": 91.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 95.80000305175781,
      "text": "Gotta feel helpless",
      "start": 94.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 123.83999633789062,
      "text": "I'm on my knees, I'm so unsteady I'm doing everything you told me not to do",
      "start": 117.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 127.73999786376953,
      "text": "I knew you were right, I knew I was wrong But I still said, fuck that, I'm gone",
      "start": 123.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 133.16000366210938,
      "text": "So come back to me, Succubus And make me the way you thought I should be",
      "start": 127.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 137.44000244140625,
      "text": "I need help with me Come back, Succubus",
      "start": 133.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 141.25999450683594,
      "text": "Please come back I need help with me",
      "start": 137.75999450683594
